RSI MA is a simple but really good strategy

-LOGIC-

If the RSI MA crosses above the RSI thereshold it goes long
basicly

-FEATURES-

-propare backtest table
-RSI lenght
-RSI thereshold
-many MAs to choose from
-can select long only, short only or long and short signal generation

-DOES IT WORK?-

i managed to get 1.4 sharpe, 1.5 omega and a maxdd of 12% on really volitile assets like BTC
for less volitile assets it worked even better


